Interface IJGenerifiable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJGenerifiableImpl, JAnonymousClass, JDefinedClass, JMethod

    public interface IJGenerifiable
    Declarations that can have type variables. Something that can be made into a generic.
